snippet.title: Madou Monogatari: Michikusa Ibun - Part 1
snippet.description:
This is the Madou game that connects the Madou series and the Puyo Puyo series.  Let's see if I can get through it (probably not).

Starting off with grinding and wandering always seems to be the way to go.
